replies.body:
I saw a quote from one of the people defending him that made me sick to my stomach:
"Everyone is toxic; we all get pissed at shitty teammates that feed and suck dick."

That's just absurd. {{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}}

I watched one as well. I don't want someone like that playing on my team...

...but part of me knows that it can't be helped. There's a lot of players out there who are just like him, yet they don't have channels that people can watch. He's like one of them.

I really don't know how people think his stuff is funny... they wouldn't be laughing if they were playing with him... {{champion:32}} {{item:3070}}
